ActCanada Pension Plan
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADA PENSION PLAN REGULATIONS by excepting employment where the employee is appointed by the Government of Manitoba to a board, commission or committee and is paid a retainer, an honoraruim or on a fee basis, from being considered as pensionable employment.
